        <item>
            <title>黃仁勳到訪台中夜市，被人潮所限空手而回</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/18/jensen-huang-taichung/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=jensen-huang-taichung</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/18/jensen-huang-taichung/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 11:00:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NVIDIA]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[台中]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[黃仁勳]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287628</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>NVIDIA 總裁黃仁勳對於台灣夜市情有獨鍾，之前曾現身台北的夜市，最近他首次造訪台中，同樣前往當地著名逢甲夜市，不過卻遇到大批羣組，場面混亂之下也無法繼續行程。<br /><span id="more-1287628"></span></p><p>晚上黃仁勳原定前往逢甲夜市品嚐美食，但因現場湧入大批粉絲，場面一度失控。短短 30 米的路程，他走了長達 40 分鐘，最終為避免發生踩踏事故，不得不提前結束行程。有消息更指現場曾出現索取利是等不當行為，引起爭議。</p><p>對於此次夜市行程受阻，黃仁勳幽默地回應指：「這次在台中逛夜市不要説吃了，連走進夜市都很難。」他期待未來能再次造訪：「你們告訴我你們哪天不去，這樣我就有機會去逛了！」對於總部選址台中的可能性，他以台語回應「當然有啊！」，並表示正在尋找合適的地點設立「非常漂亮的總部」。</p><p>黃仁勳此行除了訪問矽品新廠外，還與台積電董事長魏哲家共進午餐，並出席緯創和 NVIDIA 的尾牙活動。他強調 NVIDIA 在台灣持續成長，需要更大的場地，歡迎各界提供合適的地點建議，展現 NVIDIA 深耕台灣市場的決心。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://today.line.me/tw/v2/article/9mWkp5g">太報</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/18/jensen-huang-taichung/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Casio 全新設計太陽能環保計數機，太陽能板放機頂提升美感</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/18/casio-comfy-jt-200t/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=casio-comfy-jt-200t</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/18/casio-comfy-jt-200t/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 10:00:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[gadgets]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CASIO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[計數機]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287568</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>信大家都曾經用過 Casio 計數機，有沒有覺得其機面的太陽能板非常礙眼？為提升計數機美感，Casio 日本公司宣佈本月將會推出全新太陽能計數機 Comfy JT-200T，售價為 3,850 日圓（約港幣 193 元），全新設計的 Comfy JT-200T 特意將太陽能板放在機頂位置，一改以往置於機面之設計。Comfy JT-200T 以環保材料與經典設計為核心特色，集實用性與美學於一身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287578" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t00sc-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t00sc-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t00sc.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yGHR312sjU&amp;ab_channel=CASIOJapan">CASIO Japan@YouTube</a></p><div class="flex-1 overflow-hidden @container/thread"><div class="h-full"><div class="react-scroll-to-bottom--css-ybehe-79elbk h-full"><div class="react-scroll-to-bottom--css-ybehe-1n7m0yu"><div class="flex flex-col text-sm md:pb-9"><article class="w-full scroll-mb-[var(--thread-trailing-height,150px)] text-token-text-primary focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-[-4px]" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-21" data-scroll-anchor="true"><div class="m-auto text-base py-[18px] px-3 md:px-4 w-full md:px-5 lg:px-4 xl:px-5"><div class="mx-auto flex flex-1 gap-4 text-base md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 md:max-w-3xl lg:max-w-[40rem] xl:max-w-[48rem]"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"><div class="min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" dir="auto" data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="2dc06602-410c-4008-acaa-78e3948eff36" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light"><p>Comfy JT-200T 的設計結合美觀與實用性，將太陽能電池設置於機身頂部邊緣，確保能源供應穩定，同時減少視覺幹擾。這種設計提升產品整體簡潔性，保持使用時計數機視覺清晰。</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article></div></div></div></div></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287581" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t031s-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t031s-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t031s.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yGHR312sjU&amp;ab_channel=CASIOJapan">CASIO Japan@YouTube</a></p><p>機身提供五種柔和色調，包括米白、深灰、灰粉、灰綠及灰藍，用戶可隨意挑選符合個人品味的顏色。外殼採用回收塑料製成，既提升耐用性，亦有效降低對環境的負擔，展現了設計與實用的平衡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287583" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t048s-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t048s-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t048s.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲共有 5 色可選，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yGHR312sjU&amp;ab_channel=CASIOJapan">CASIO Japan@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287582" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t045s-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t045s-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t045s.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲使用 59% 再生物料製成，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yGHR312sjU&amp;ab_channel=CASIOJapan">CASIO Japan@YouTube</a></p><p>為紀念 Casio 首款計數機推出 60 週年，Comfy JT-200T 特別採用經典字體，賦予設計懷舊氣息，同時融入現代美感。這款計數機配備 12 位 LCD 熒幕，畫面清晰易讀，功能簡潔實用，並增設稅務按鈕，方便商務或個人用戶輕鬆處理稅率。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287579" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t013s-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t013s-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t013s.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yGHR312sjU&amp;ab_channel=CASIOJapan">CASIO Japan@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287580" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t016s-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t016s-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t016s.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yGHR312sjU&amp;ab_channel=CASIOJapan">CASIO Japan@YouTube</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/16/24345129/casio-japan-calculator-comfy-jt-200-design-solar-power-panel">The Verge</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yGHR312sjU&amp;ab_channel=CASIOJapan">CASIO Japan@YouTube</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
